<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Application Received</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #111827;
        }
        p {
            margin: 12px 0;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 24px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>New Review Submitted</h1>
    <p> There is a new review submitted by <strong><%= reviewerName %></strong> (<%= reviewerEmail %>).

    <div class="info-box">
        <p><span class="label">Url:</span> <%= url %></p>
    </div>

    <p>If we need more information, we’ll reach out to you via this email address.</p>

    <div class="footer">
        — FF2050.com
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
